gmobile 0.7.0
-------------
Released March 2026
* Display-panel-* helper fixes
* Display panel support for:
    * Google Pixel 6a
    * Motorola edge 30
    * Motorola Moto G7
    * SHIFT6mq
    * Fix suppport for Pixel 6 and 6 pro
* Contributors:
    * Achill Gilgenast
    * Guido Günther
    * Pedro Alves
    * Val Packett

gmobile 0.6.0
-------------
Released December 2025
* Allow for different corner radii
* Add hwdb and udev rule to configure minimum torch brightness
* Oneplus 6: Use different corner radii for top and bottom
* Leak fixes
* Issues fixed:
    * https://gitlab.gnome.org/World/Phosh/gmobile/-/issues/10
    * https://gitlab.gnome.org/World/Phosh/gmobile/-/issues/5
* Contributors:
    * Guido Günther
    * Robert Eckelmann

gmobile 0.5.0
-------------
Released November 2025
* Add display information for Fairphone 6
* Allow to run gm-display-panel-run-phosh headless allowing one to use
  the tool with compositors that restrict window sizes and in ci.
* Contributors:
    * Guido Günther
    * Luca Weiss

